
 We received the executed Assignment and Novation Agreement between HS Energy 
Services, Inc., ENA and J. Aron & Company, effective at of 12:00 p.m. on June 
28, 2000.    Under the terms of this agreement, HS Energy Services, Inc. 
assigns  to ENA all of its right, title and interest in certain Transactions 
it has entered into with J. Aron & Company.  The Transactions will be 
governed by the ISDA Master Agreement, dated as of August 14, 1994, between 
ENA and J. Aron & Company.       Copies will be distributed.





